Icons¶

Icons for GUI elements (such as GuiApi.add_button()) can be specified using the viser.Icon enum.

class viser.IconName¶

Name of an icon. Should be generated via viser.Icon.*.

alias of str

class viser.Icon[source]¶

‘Enum’ class for referencing Tabler icons.

We don’t subclass enum.Enum for performance reasons – importing an enum with thousands of names can result in import times in the hundreds of milliseconds.
